Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.45,0:00:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压抑高昂的鼓动 奔向暮色昏暗的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.36,0:00:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心和客套之间 对那家伙的想法复杂交错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.86,0:00:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有答案也无妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.74,0:00:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这份爱粉身碎骨 你的表情为何如此寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.64,0:00:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谎言 心机 嫉妒 背叛 有如家常便饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.28,0:00:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无须大惊小怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.89,0:00:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃之心点燃火苗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.96,0:00:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多想再去见你一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不行动 何时才要做呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.03,0:00:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇花开 蔷薇花落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.00,0:00:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心中有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.97,0:01:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高雅的 优美的 华丽的飞舞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.11,0:01:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇花开 蔷薇花飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.25,0:01:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼中有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.28,0:01:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用心祈祷的话 一定能改变命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.46,0:01:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧热情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.56,0:01:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活得灿烂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.63,0:01:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你同在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.97,0:01:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第11话 龙的指引

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.08,0:01:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美玉，妳的生日被搞砸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.49,0:01:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎\N反正今天的事是我所乐见的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.83,0:01:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是没想到会变成这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.46,0:01:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗传人的对战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.23,0:02:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏妳让我看到了精采场面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是拳志郎的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.06,0:02:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N而妳也一脚踏进了那个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.17,0:02:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经做好心理准备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.84,0:02:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之，妳先避避风头吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.31,0:02:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吴一定会来追杀妳的\N或许就是今晚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.45,0:02:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.82,0:02:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其被那个吴玷污\N我宁愿选择一死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.72,0:03:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的自尊心还是一样很强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.39,0:03:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我送妳一个好消息\N当生日礼物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.43,0:03:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好消息？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，这样应该就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是用木头会比较轻松吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.85,0:03:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊\N用铁块固定就完全动不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.56,0:03:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.23,0:03:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.53,0:03:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过有点难看就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.67,0:03:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前在上海修行拳法时\N也都是这样疗伤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.51,0:03:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.34,0:03:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手会断掉的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.58,0:03:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说会痛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.65,0:04:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系，至少我知道潘在哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.43,0:04:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没死？那个人还活着？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.36,0:04:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，妳的情人潘光琳并没有死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人…还活着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，他人在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.72,0:04:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不远了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.22,0:04:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵王说他两小时前才见过潘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.56,0:04:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他打斗时闻到了潘的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能确定潘还没死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.47,0:04:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…\N光凭你像狗的鼻子还是不够吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.88,0:05:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.15,0:05:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先，灵王身上传出了水的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水的味道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.95,0:05:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是黄埔江那种大河的水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.52,0:05:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，那是苏州河的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.36,0:05:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后，还有线香的味道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是坟墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.97,0:05:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吴东来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.14,0:05:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪处坟墓是跟他有关的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.48,0:05:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坟墓？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.34,0:05:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟女星狂有关的坟墓…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.58,0:05:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女星狂…爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.32,0:05:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得之前自杀的红星林磷夕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.42,0:05:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吴东来超迷她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.52,0:05:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对喔，吴东来的怪异性癖好\N把磷夕逼到自杀身亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.43,0:05:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果他还把自家祖坟迁到\N她的墓地旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.23,0:05:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.13,0:05:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠近苏州河畔\N新闸附近新辟的墓地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.77,0:05:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是公肇山庄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.86,0:06:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的确有可能用来囚禁潘老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.36,0:06:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.96,0:06:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳，爸爸，我们快去公肇山庄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.83,0:06:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.33,0:06:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.60,0:06:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不行呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.47,0:06:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊，好不容易掌握了位置耶\N为什么不去呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.11,0:06:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不去？拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.72,0:06:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个混帐说美玉爱上老子的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.62,0:06:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.36,0:06:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为何阎王会出现在大戏院里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.26,0:07:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太可疑了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说老子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.21,0:07:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.08,0:07:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被他们摆一道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.88,0:07:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美玉和阎王根本是同伙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.88,0:07:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们马上去把美玉抓过来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.09,0:07:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死定了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个好点子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.07,0:07:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没下厨做菜啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.24,0:07:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不…不会吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大要下厨？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.07,0:07:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美玉难得过生日啊\N我要送上亲手做的料理给她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.55,0:07:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快去给我准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.48,0:07:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.82,0:08:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其被做成那种料理…\N还不如死了算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.43,0:08:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着瞧吧，美玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.67,0:08:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N那美玉可能也会有危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.54,0:08:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N不知道吴下一步会怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.01,0:08:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上还有一个灵王…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.31,0:08:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道吴的动向\N我们是无法随便出手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们到底该去哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.71,0:08:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去救潘老大？\N还是去保护美玉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.99,0:08:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳，你说话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳，那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.43,0:08:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗龙盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.73,0:08:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是以前有一位精通\N密教占星术的道士给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.74,0:08:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他教我遇到问题时\N可以问问这条龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.58,0:08:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时，有一次我正在修练拳法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.08,0:09:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果受了重伤，动弹不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷子你有事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脸上有怪东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.96,0:09:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不出来，看不出来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.03,0:09:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的面相真是不可思议啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.33,0:09:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不出来你的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.91,0:10:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老道，我的面相有那么惨吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有，我不是这个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.75,0:10:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间的宿命是无法任意改变的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.66,0:10:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个村子以前热闹富庶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.16,0:10:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却也难以抵抗宿命\N而变成这副寂寥的模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过人的命运却可以改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.40,0:10:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要施一点小法术就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.77,0:10:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你的面相显示出\N你的命运可以自由改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.64,0:10:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才说我看不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.58,0:10:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个老道难不成知道\N我是北斗的传人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.32,0:10:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你一副不知所措的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.59,0:10:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，这个你拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.23,0:10:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是罗龙盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.20,0:11:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后当你不知何去何从之时\N就问问这条龙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.27,0:11:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是就是正面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否会出现反面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.91,0:11:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…\N我没有道理接受你的馈赠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.12,0:11:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说了\N没道理，但是有缘份啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.29,0:11:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听好，能改变命运的就是缘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.96,0:11:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要诚心祈祷就能遇到有缘人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.93,0:11:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在祈祷…\N“我想遇见北斗的传人”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.44,0:11:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老道你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗的传人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.37,0:11:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你有趟美好的命运之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.33,0:11:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指示去路的神奇罗龙盘啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.71,0:12:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要试试看？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.61,0:12:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.81,0:12:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也许就是道士口中\N我该向罗龙盘询问去向的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.86,0:12:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去救潘，答案为是或否
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.87,0:13:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是正面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.31,0:13:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，去公肇山庄\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去救潘出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.05,0:13:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.79,0:13:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.26,0:13:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，前面好像有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.67,0:13:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的表情还真恐怖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.67,0:13:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳，你认识他吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.94,0:13:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的右手应该也断了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还有本事来这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.21,0:13:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么还笑得出来啊\N现在该怎么办才好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.71,0:14:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他是不打算让我们过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.36,0:14:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.43,0:14:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对喔，撞过去就对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.03,0:14:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.84,0:14:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死的话就闪边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.04,0:14:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，他不躲开吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.88,0:14:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想死啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手臂包得比我还粗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.79,0:14:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快撞到了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.96,0:14:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.80,0:14:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是何方神圣啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.37,0:14:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是灵王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.70,0:14:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你干嘛不早点讲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.17,0:14:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙是想去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.21,0:15:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，我先去解决另一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.66,0:15:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳志郎现在应该已经去救潘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.93,0:15:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作不快点\N潘可能今晚就会被杀死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.37,0:15:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.24,0:15:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为妳只爱潘一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吴为此而心生怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.41,0:15:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此他故意不杀潘\N一直折磨他到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.75,0:15:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像开始了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.06,0:16:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讨厌处理善后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.73,0:16:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不想看“那个”的装盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.07,0:16:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想早点回家喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.44,0:16:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘，你知道今天是什么日子吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.81,0:16:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，今天是美玉的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.18,0:16:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆生宴上必须端上最好的菜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.79,0:16:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想替美玉做一道“龙虎斗”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.96,0:16:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？很棒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.13,0:17:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.87,0:17:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想提醒我龙虎斗少了虎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.87,0:17:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你够细心，的确是少了一只虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.44,0:17:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.78,0:17:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样料理不算是完成耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.71,0:17:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，你不用操心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.32,0:17:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有现成的“虎”了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.92,0:17:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，今日的龙虎斗的主菜\N是人称上海之虎的潘光琳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的人头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.86,0:17:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样，龙虎斗就算是完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.26,0:17:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想早点看到美玉毫不知情\N开心吃下去的表情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.24,0:17:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.95,0:17:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装饰得真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.98,0:17:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，开始做菜啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在笑什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.43,0:18:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在对美玉纠缠不休啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.93,0:18:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘，这种好女人配你太浪费了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.00,0:18:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以料理上桌后\N我要去好好的疼爱她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.98,0:18:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想得美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.21,0:18:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.28,0:18:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不明白吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.72,0:18:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来告诉你好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.88,0:18:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是脸的问题，是脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.75,0:18:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美玉只爱帅哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.19,0:18:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能正常分辨出\N哪种人才是美男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.63,0:18:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢？请问你是帅哥吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.77,0:18:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我比起来，你能看吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.81,0:18:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道差别了吧？\N我们之间的差别…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吴东来，你听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.75,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的行为会决定他的外表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.78,0:19:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的长相反应了你的丑陋行径
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.82,0:19:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快动手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.56,0:19:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则我都快笑死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.86,0:19:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅哥就算死了还是帅哥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.03,0:19:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你活得不耐烦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直提什么长相…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.44,0:19:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你下油锅…很烫的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.38,0:19:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的嫉妒真是让人看不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.68,0:19:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.05,0:19:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.79,0:19:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们怎么都被下油锅啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.46,0:19:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.63,0:19:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面粉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理的时间到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主菜是炸海狮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.57,0:19:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阎王…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.05,0:20:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吴东来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.39,0:20:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视我的警告还敢留在上海\N你一定会后悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.56,0:20:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你口气倒是很大嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.00,0:20:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我一枪毙了潘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.94,0:20:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样啊，阎王\N我看后悔莫及的人是你啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.21,0:20:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪啊，有种就杀了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.68,0:20:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我活不久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.28,0:20:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临死前能够见到拳志郎\N我死而无憾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.65,0:20:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友真是不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.02,0:20:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人动容啊，阎王\N你忍心对好朋友见死不救吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.06,0:20:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.90,0:20:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.53,0:21:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你动手没关系\N反正接着就轮到你去死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.47,0:21:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定？我真的会扣扳机喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快杀啊，猪头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快杀啊，猪头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.38,0:21:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣下扳机我就死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.25,0:21:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不能在这里示弱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.82,0:21:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好，我来真的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.13,0:21:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的，真的，真的喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.03,0:21:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.07,0:21:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，混帐，混帐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.54,0:21:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.14,0:21:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跑去哪了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.57,0:21:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可恶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.47,0:21:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管了，我先毙了潘再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.05,0:21:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小鬼是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.68,0:21:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，现在轮到我上场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.89,0:21:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.93,0:21:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙交给我来收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.36,0:22:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是叶吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.53,0:22:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.57,0:22:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把老大折磨成这样\N我绝对不放过他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.97,0:22:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N清一下你多日来的积怨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.04,0:22:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吴东来，去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.95,0:22:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.85,0:22:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.32,0:22:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是怎么了？\N吴竟然可以快速移动…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.06,0:22:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓到了吧，其实我可以行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.33,0:22:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见识一下我这个秘密武器吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.77,0:22:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然暗藏了这招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.67,0:22:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也太神奇了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.54,0:22:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个发明可以让我的动作\N快到连眼睛都跟不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.84,0:22:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的人是你们啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.18,0:22:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳，怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.75,0:22:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阎王你说话啊\N我的动作快到你看不见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.05,0:22:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是敢戳我的穴道\N我马上就剁掉你的手指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.39,0:23:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样，怎么样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.09,0:23:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戳得到穴道就来戳看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.97,0:23:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了，这样的话\N脚上的机关就用不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.38,0:23:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手，不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.98,0:23:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对秘孔有意见的话就冲着我来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.29,0:23:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连被点穴的价值都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.86,0:23:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吴东来…不，炸海狮完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.23,0:23:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了，这种菜没人想吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.74,0:23:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想念你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.24,0:23:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了，朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.39,0:24:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂静安眠的城市中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.66,0:24:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不禁陷入深深沉思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.66,0:24:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有许多琐碎的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.57,0:24:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没错过妳瞬间的不安神情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.37,0:24:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问妳是不是已经不再爱我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.44,0:24:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有答案就等于是答案了吧
